name: AbJo - The AbJonian Suite, Vol. III (Mini-Mix #2)

metadata.description:
This is yet another rare mini-mix (played and recorded live!) that features rare and unreleased beats/tracks that may or may not be included in my next beat tape-in-progress, "The AbJonian Suite Tape". This counts as the 3rd volume of beats in the series of compilations I've curated, affectionately called "The AbJonian Suite", the continuous career-long, active portfolio of ideas/beats that I consider to be some of my favorites as well as my best.

I want to personally thank Sound, David, Iman and team, and all of my collectors so far for your support and patronage of me, and like always, I dedicate this one to ya'll üôèüèΩü§üüèΩ...
